<p>This tab lists the users whose bounce count is greater than 0.</p><table><tr><td>User email</td><td>The email address of the user. This is a link to the user page.</td></tr><tr><td>Bounce count</td><td>The number of bounces on the email address. This is the same value as shown on the user details page.</td></tr><tr><td>Confirmed</td><td>An icon is displayed if the email address is unconfirmed.</td></tr><tr><td>Blacklisted</td><td>Displays an icon if the subscriber is blacklisted or if the email address is blacklisted.</td></tr></table>